---
const features = [
  { blob: "/images/wpi/connector.png",  icon: "/images/wpi/icon-insights.svg",  label: "Insights\ninternacionais" },
  { blob: "/images/wpi/connector.png",  icon: "/images/wpi/icon-parcerias.svg", label: "Parcerias\nglobais" },
  { blob: "/images/wpi/connector2.png", icon: "/images/wpi/icon-troca.svg",     label: "Troca de\nexperiências" },
  { blob: "/images/wpi/connector.png",  icon: "/images/wpi/icon-squads.svg",    label: "Squads com\nespecialistas" },
];
---

<section class="wpi-pratica">
  <h2 class="wpi-pratica__title">O que isso significa na prática?</h2>
  <div class="wpi-pratica__features">
    {features.map((f) => (
      <div class="wpi-pratica__feature">
        <div class="wpi-pratica__icon-wrap">
          <img src={f.blob} alt="" class="wpi-pratica__blob" aria-hidden="true" />
          <img src={f.icon} alt="" class="wpi-pratica__icon" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <p class="wpi-pratica__label">{f.label}</p>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <p class="wpi-pratica__body">
    Acesso a dados, referências e especialistas do mundo inteiro para ampliar estratégia, escala e resultado.
  </p>

  <h3 class="wpi-pratica__quote">
    Porque quando a visão se expande,<br>o impacto cresce.
  </h3>
</section>

<style>
  .wpi-pratica {
    background-color: #030303;
    background-image: url('/images/degrade-pixels.png');
    background-size: auto;
    background-repeat: repeat-x;
    background-position: 0 center;
    background-blend-mode: hard-light;
    animation: bg-pan-x 240s linear infinite;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 100px 165px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 80px;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8.33vw, 7.5rem);
    line-height: 0.9625;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__feature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__icon-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
  }

  @keyframes blob-float {
    0%   { transform: scale(1)    rotate(0deg)   translate(0px, 0px); }
    25%  { transform: scale(1.04) rotate(4deg)   translate(2px, -3px); }
    50%  { transform: scale(0.97) rotate(-2deg)  translate(-2px, 2px); }
    75%  { transform: scale(1.03) rotate(3deg)   translate(1px, -2px); }
    100% { transform: scale(1)    rotate(0deg)   translate(0px, 0px); }
  }

  .wpi-pratica__blob {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    animation: blob-float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform-origin: center;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__feature:nth-child(2) .wpi-pratica__blob { animation-delay: -1.5s; animation-duration: 7s; }
  .wpi-pratica__feature:nth-child(3) .wpi-pratica__blob { animation-delay: -3s;   animation-duration: 5.5s; }
  .wpi-pratica__feature:nth-child(4) .wpi-pratica__blob { animation-delay: -4.5s; animation-duration: 6.5s; }

  .wpi-pratica__icon {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 22%;
    width: 56%;
    height: 56%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.9vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
    white-space: pre-line;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.08vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .wpi-pratica__quote {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 4.69vw, 5.625rem);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .wpi-pratica {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .wpi-pratica__title {
      white-space: normal;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3.5rem);
    }

    .wpi-pratica__features {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .wpi-pratica__icon-wrap {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
    }
  }
</style>
